    {
      "title": "Vendor Plans - Pricing - Ordering Information",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Instructions",
          "id": "heading-3"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Customers will process all cellular requests through the",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            },
            {
              "href": "https://itservices.nc.gov/services/collaboration-communication/cellular-telephone",
              "text": " ITS Service Catalog",
              "opens_new_window": true
            },
            {
              "text": " in which you can access each vendor’s web site by clicking on the Vendor’s name. These requests include but are not limited to: provisioning of new equipment and service plan; add, change, suspend or cancel an existing plan, and port cellular services. The Vendor web sites provide information on the service plans that include cost and service parameters as well as coverage maps. ",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            },
            {
              "text": "In order to complete any process from the Vendor web site, customers must have their Department Code and Vendor Account Code. The Department Code, consisting of sixteen (16) digits, and the Vendor Account Code can be found on the detailed portion of an existing cellular phone bill.",
              "bold": true,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            },
            {
              "text": " If a customer does not have any existing service with Information Technology Services, they may contact the ITS Service Desk at 919-754-6000 or toll free at 1-800-722-3926 for instructions on establishing a Department Code and/or Vendor Account Code.",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Please Note:",
              "bold": true,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            },
            {
              "text": " Netbooks and iPads are available under this contract only if a corresponding data/service plan is included with the device.",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "To obtain contract information or access Vendor’s website,",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false
            },
            {
              "href": "https://it.nc.gov/services/service-directory/telephony/cellular-telephone",
              "text": " CLICK HERE",
